Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:

Situated in the heart of the parliamentary precinct, 15 National Circuit is within proximity to major departments such as DFAT, Prime Minister and Cabinet as well as major privates such as IBM and PWC.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
10 National Circuit is ideally located in the heart of Barton and near the Parliamentary Triangle. This spectacular B Grade 4 level office building consists of a modern design, high functioning facilities including lifts that service to all four floors, showers, disabled toilets and a ground floor cafe. 

10 National Circuit is a short distance from the CBD, Kingston and Manuka. This prime location provides access to a variety of amenity and some of Canberra's best eateries.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: REFURBISHED OFFICE - GREAT LOCATION IN BARTON

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
55 Blackall Street is located in the heart of Barton next to the parliamentary triangle.  Only a short drive to the Canberra CBD & Airport, this is a premium location for a range of businesses.  With Boeing a major tenant in the building, this is an excellent corporate location.  Staff can benefit from a short walk to Lake Burley Griffin with nearby amenity available.

The building itself is 7,700sqm* over six levels which has undergone major refurbishments including a new entry foyer, lift lobbies, floor plates and amenity.  The building features showers, lockers and bike storage, 117 basement parking spaces and good natural light from all elevations.

Availability:

Level 3 - 242sqm* High quality fitout in place, available March 2021. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*Approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: HIGH QUALITY OFFICE ACCOMMODATION - LAST REMAINING SUITE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
42 Macquarie Street is situated within the Barton precinct, in the heart of the Parliamentary Triangle. The building has undergone an extensive refurbishment program including brand new lobby and refurbished floor plates with new ceiling, lighting and floor coverings.  The building offers amenity for staff including shower facilities and bike storage.

Surrounded by an abundance of amenity including modern food and beverage offerings, gyms, childcare centre and only a short distance to the Canberra City Centre, the building is ideally located to suit a variety of occupants. The building has excellent parking ratios, with all day parking options available close by as well as public transport.

A range of high quality office spaces are available to meet a range of requirements.

Level 1, Suite 1 - 218sqm*
- New fit out with waiting area, 8 person boardroom, 1x meeting room, 1x office, 1x call room, collaborative area, utilities area, large breakout area and 20 open plan sit to stand workstations.
- Unit features high ceilings with excellent natural light.

Level 1, Suite 3 - 253sqm*
- New fit out with waiting area, 10 person boardroom, 1 meeting room, 1x exec office/meeting room, 4x offices, collaborative areas, utilities area, large breakout area and 15 open plan sit to stand workstations.
- Unit features high ceilings with excellent natural light.

Level 4 whole floor - 975sqm* 
- Exclusive whole top floor available for lease Q4 2021.
- Floor to be refurbished back to base ready for fit out.
- Excellent outlooks towards parliament house and natural light.
- Access to private balcony

Please contact the exclusive marketing agents for the available areas, prices and inspections.
